.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNHM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c758%2c20220928%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNHM,111,聲,758,20220928,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"758","JDATE":"20220928","JTITLE":"聲請定應執行之刑並諭知易科罰"}